    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely dice your <strong>red onion[s]</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>red chilli[es]</strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop finely</p><p>Strip your <strong>mint leaves </strong>from their stems and chop them finely, discard the stems</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
